                    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;) WITH COMPACT STORAGE&quot;&lt;/span&gt; +
                    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    AND CLUSTERING ORDER BY (b DESC)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);

